rows.label: qst104303_msg001
rows.name: Do you have business with Melolo, mo?

rows.label: qst104303_msg001_1
rows.name: Rex, what brings you here today, mo?

rows.label: qst104303_msg003
rows.name:
Melolo has heard of it, mo. But
it's an unofficial thing that
happens behind the scenes, mo.

rows.label: qst104303_msg004
rows.name:
It's not good to spread it around,
but this time is special, mo.

rows.label: qst104303_msg005
rows.name:
However, Melolo doesn't know
much about it either, mo.

rows.label: qst104303_msg006
rows.name:
Melolo heard a rumor that someone
named Limlim does the ranking, so
you should go meet them and ask, mo.

rows.label: qst104303_msg007
rows.name:
Oh, and since this ranking is
unofficial, it's forbidden to
talk about it openly, mo!
